 Remix Heart manga, and additional scenarios for certain characters such as Kokonoe, Kagura, and Bullet. For the localized version of Extend, Library Mode reintroduced from the Japanese release. The Playstation Vita version of Chrono Phantasma Extend also adds dual audio to the Story Mode, which was not present in the original Vita release.","total_rating":87.29013998083997,"total_rating_count":21,"url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/blazblue-chrono-phantasma-extend","videos":[{"id":4951,"video_id":"6RwMVaug31A"},{"id":4952,"video_id":"wRTFuiK9hgc"},{"id":62317,"video_id":"haBwlyYgLpA"},{"id":62318,"video_id":"MbUyXqp6Rko"}],"websites":[{"id":341707,"url":"https://www.twitch.tv/directory/game/BlazBlue:%20Chrono%20Phantasma%20Extend","type":{"id":6,"type":"Twitch"}},{"id":112312,"url":"https://store.steampowered.com/app/388750/BlazBlue_Chronophantasma_Extend/","type":{"id":13,"type":"Steam"}},{"id":755603,"url":"https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/228310","type":{"id":23,"type":"Playstation"}},{"id":755602,"url":"https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/blazblue-chronophantasma-extend/BS41PBV1CZSN","type":{"id":22,"type":"Xbox"}},{"id":4014,"url":"http://www.blazblue.jp/cp/special_extend.html","type":{"id":1,"type":"Official Website"}}]}